lyrics:
[verse]
Elias and Bobo, friends so true
Embark on adventures, away they flew
Exploring the world, with hearts so pure
Together they'll conquer, of that they're sure

[chorus]
Elias und Bobo, on Abenteuertour
With laughter and joy, their spirits will soar
Hand in hand, they'll face all the unknown
Bound by friendship, forever they'll roam
